snippet.title: Last Moon - Early Footage
snippet.description:
Last Moon is an Action RPG in development inspired by the great RPGs from the 90' like Legend of Zelda, Secret of Mana, Chrono Trigger, and a lot of more!

Find more info about the game : 

Website : http://skoll-studio.com/lastmoon.html
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/LastMoonTheGame
Twitter : https://twitter.com/LastMoonGame
